exp4j - ${project-version}
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

exp4j math expression evaluator for the Java programming language, capable of evaluating simple mathematical 
expression, only 24kb in size, without any external libraries and simple to use:

Calculatable calc = new ExpressionBuilder("7*x + 3*y - log(y/x*12)^y")
							.withVariable("x", varX)
							.withVariable("y", varY)
							.build();
double result = calc.calculate();

exp4j requires at least Java 5